title: EMC Isilon NFS- and system-statistics information
agents: isilon
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors EMC Isilon cluster statistics. Status will be {WARN} if
 network packet errors occur. The checks monitors NFSv3 iops, OneFS bandwidth
 read/write, network bandwidth, packets and errors for in- and outbound traffic, 
 disk iops and disk bandwidth read/write.

 A perfometer is provided, that shows NFS iops.

inventory:
 One service per Isilon cluster is created.

item:
 Isilon Statistics <Isilon Clustername>
